Class PlayerDatas

  • java.lang.Object
    • dataBase.PlayerDatas

  • public class PlayerDatas
extends java.lang.Object
    This class handles all data like names, color and time for each player. If any other class wants to know something about the players, it has to call a getter of this class.
    Author:
    Timon Borter
